Que 13) Explain the Grid System in Bootstrap?
----------------------------------------------
Bootstrap grid system is used to create layout using rows and columns.
It is based on 12 columns
Uses classes like row, col
Helps in making responsive layouts
Example:
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-6">Left</div>
  <div class="col-6">Right</div>
</div>

Que 14) What is the difference between col-xs, col-sm, col-md, col-lg & col-xl?
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These classes define layout for different screen sizes:
Class	Screen Size
col-xs	Extra small (phones)
col-sm	Small devices (≥576px)
col-md	Medium devices (≥768px)
col-lg	Large devices (≥992px)
col-xl	Extra large devices (≥1200px)
👉 Note: col-xs is not used in Bootstrap 4/5

